intent.user_query: What are the top 5 most frequently purchased product brands to target for marketing campaigns?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT p.Brand, SUM(sd.Quantity) AS TotalQuantitySold FROM fitness_db.SaleDetails sd JOIN fitness_db.Products p ON sd.ProductID = p.ProductID GROUP BY p.Brand ORDER BY TotalQuantitySold DESC LIMIT 5;

arguments.sql: SELECT p.Brand, SUM(sd.Quantity) AS TotalQuantitySold FROM fitness_db.SaleDetails sd JOIN fitness_db.Products p ON sd.ProductID = p.ProductID GROUP BY p.Brand ORDER BY TotalQuantitySold DESC LIMIT 5;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
